.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, light-blue, lilac, brown
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who likes brown is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the person who likes red is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | lilac   | light-blue         | brown   | red    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

