.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, broccoli, cabbage, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person eating nectarine is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating broccoli##7
2. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person eating nectarine is somewhere between the person eating cabbage and the person eating cherry##7
4. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person eating cherry##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | broccoli   | cabbage | nectarine | cherry    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

