.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, train, car
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
6. the person driving the car is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the person driving the car is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Transport          | car | quad-bike | taxi  | train |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

