.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, mouse, fish
1. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person drinking water and the owner of the mouse##7
3. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
4. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the owner of the dog##8
5. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Pet      | dog | mouse | fish  | lizard |

