4. the fan of country is somewhere between the fan of metal and the dressmaker##7
5. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the project-manager##8
6. the project-manager is somewhere between the fan of metal and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | country        | jazz          | metal |

