.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bongani, tiparillo, davidoff
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the dannemann-smoker##2
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
5. the bongani-smoker is the bongani-smoker##1
6. the fan of indie is not the tiparillo-smoker##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Cigar     | davidoff | bongani       | dannemann  | tiparillo    |

