4. the manager is not to the right of the chef##8
5. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the chef##3
6. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the person who likes purple##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job         | manager | chef      | writer   | librarian  |
| Color   | blood-red    | emerald | purple | fuchsia |

