.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, onion, pineapple
House: townhouse, victorian, craftsman, cottage
1. the person eating onion is not to the right of the cottage house##8
2. the townhouse house is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the townhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the cottage house and the craftsman house##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the cottage house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime        | pineapple | onion      | corn    |
| House   | townhouse | craftsman   | victorian | cottage |

