.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, juice, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: cat, snake, lizard, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
2. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta         | juice    | cola       |
| Pet      | snake | turtle | cat | lizard |

