.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
4 different games are played: bridge, canasta, chess, whist
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
2. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
4. the person playing canasta is between the person playing whist and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Game   | bridge     | canasta | whist        | chess       |
| Hobby      | drawing | collecting  | card-games | magic-tricks |

