.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, juice
 1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | juice  | sprite     | lemonade    |

