2. the person who likes mauve is not to the right of the person who likes coral##8
3. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who likes coral##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
7. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3     |    4    |
| Color    | mauve   | coral    | light-blue   | ebony |
| Hobby   | cooking | photography | skydiving | dancing |

