.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, collecting, fishing, skydiving
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, jet-ski, trike
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
5. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby         | singing  | skydiving | collecting  | fishing  |
| Transport   | bike | car   | trike | jet-ski |

